Volumes Notes
1. docker saves all it's data under /var/lib/docker
2. you manage volume by run "docker volume"
3. to use volume mount "docker run -v <volumename>:<contairpath>"


Network Notes
1. Bridge network, host network, none network
2. you manage network by run "docker network"
3. to connect a container to a network "docker run --network <networkname>


CMD vs Entrypoint Notes
1. Entrypoint can'e be overwritten ( can only by --entrypoint option)
2. CMD can be overwritten 
3. when come together CMD act as argument to Entrypoint


containers registries
1.  <registry url>/<namespace>/<repo>:<tag>
